      <p><strong>Cipriani Residences Miami</strong> rises in Brickell, just minutes from Miami Beach and Key Biscayne. The tower brings the legendary Cipriani service standardborn in Harrys Bar in 1931to a modern collection of residences with intuitive, white-glove hospitality.</p>
